Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:50.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}單憑言語過於危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}避免無謀之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:57.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}正視自己 站起身來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:00.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}定能奮戰下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:04.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}祈禱著 想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}因為我曾發誓要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:12.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}即使面對絕望之路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}仍要不斷前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}想守護的 寶貴之物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:21.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fnFOT-UDMincho Pr6N DB}鼓舞人心
